# Exclude local-only env files that contain dev-only settings (e.g. NEXT_PUBLIC_SSI_WS_URL).
# These must never be bundled into cloud images — NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars baked in at build time
# would point services at localhost and break SSE/WebSocket transport in GCP Cloud Run.
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.git
**/dist
